title: I (2014) Tamil Songs 320kbps
description:
I is the soundtrack album of the upcoming 2014 Indian Tamil romantic action thriller film of the same name written and directed by S. Shankar. A. R. Rahman has composed the original songs and background score for the film. Madhan Karky and Kabilan wrote three songs each for the soundtrack album. The album consists of seven tracks, which include a remix and a reprise. The soundtrack album released on 15 September 2014. It was released digitally on iTunes and topped the iTunes India charts within seconds
